Mopani Pharmacy drew the winner for the Win a Car Competition last Thursday, and one lucky winner drove away in a brand-new Polo Vivo. The finalists gathered at Alan Hudson Motors in Riverside on June 3, where they went through processes of elimination before a final winner was drawn. Read Thurday’s Lowvelder for the full story and to find out who the winner of the car is. ALSO READ: Police officers arrested for allegedly soliciting bribe from rape-accused